-- ds.page.body:

You can create your documentation web-sites using `midnight-storm`. `midnight-storm` also
helps authors, entrepreneurs, corporate groups and bloggers to create their own
fastn web project.

-- ds.h3: 🎨 Creating fastn web-site using `midnight-storm`
id: creating-fastn-web-site-using-midnight-storm

Please, refer [this documentation](https://fastn.com/github-pages/) to
understand how to create fastn website repository on GitHub.

