-- ds.h3: 🌟 Whats next?
id: what-next

`-- page` component comes with inbuit navbar, sidebar and body content area.
Start creating new `.ftd` files inside your project and use `midnight-storm` `page`
component to write your documentation, blog posts etc.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/midnight-storm/page/) to know more
details of `page` component.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/midnight-storm/sitemap/) to learn how
to generate better `sitemap` for navigation.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/midnight-storm/types/) to know
more details of inbuit `typography`.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/midnight-storm/markdown/) to know
about markdown.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/midnight-storm/seo/) to know about
SEO support.

✨ [Click here](https://fastn-community.github.io/midnight-storm/assets/) to know about
Static Assets.

